avid-Becker-Formula-1_Formula-1-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这个神秘团体使用 PVC 管和桶鼓来演奏 emo 歌曲</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-blue-man-group-cover-my-chemical-romances-welcome-to-the-black-parade-after-one-listen-3784575">观看 Blue Man Group 翻唱 My Chemical Romance 的“Welcome to the Black Parade”后，</a>先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上听一听。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Gerard-Way-of-My-Chemical-Romance-and-Blue-Man-Group.-Credit_-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-and-David-Becker-Formula-1_Formula-1-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《我的化学浪漫》和《蓝人乐队》的杰拉德·韦 (Gerard Way)。图片来源：Ethan Miller/Getty Images 和 David Becker - Formula 1/Formula 1 via Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Gerard-Way-of-My-Chemical-Romance-and-Blue-Man-Group.-Credit_-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-and-David-Becker-Formula-1_Formula-1-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Gerard-Way-of-My-Chemical-Romance-and-Blue-Man-Group.-Credit_-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-and-David-Becker-Formula-1_Formula-1-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Gerard-Way-of-My-Chemical-Romance-and-Blue-Man-Group.-Credit_-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-and-David-Becker-Formula-1_Formula-1-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Gerard-Way-of-My-Chemical-Romance-and-Blue-Man-Group.-Credit_-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-and-David-Becker-Formula-1_Formula-1-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Gerard-Way-of-My-Chemical-Romance-and-Blue-Man-Group.-Credit_-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-and-David-Becker-Formula-1_Formula-1-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Gerard-Way-of-My-Chemical-Romance-and-Blue-Man-Group.-Credit_-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-and-David-Becker-Formula-1_Formula-1-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Blue Man Group 最近混乱地演绎了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/my-chemical-romance">My Chemical Romance</a>的“Welcome to the Black Parade”。看看下面。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-listid="30"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/my-chemical-romance-new-song-the-foundations-of-decay-3224859"><b>My Chemical Romance 的新歌“The Foundations of Decay”是一次激烈、无畏的回归</b></a></li></ul><p>这一尝试是在这个神秘乐队出现在 Drumeo 正在进行的<em>《第一次》</em>系列的最新一集中时进行的，在该节目中，名人面孔走进录音室，并试图在第一次听到歌曲时立即用鼓演奏歌曲。</p><p>在之前的剧集中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-red-hot-chili-peppers-chad-smith-drum-along-to-bring-me-the-horizons-can-you-feel-my-heart-hearing-it-for-the-first-time-3780996">，Red Hot Chili Peppers 的 Chad Smith 曾用鼓声伴奏 Bring Me The Horizo​​n 的“Can You Feel My Heart”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-chad-smith-play-thirty-seconds-to-mars-the-kill-as-he-hears-it-for-the-first-time-3502905">三十秒上火星的“The Kill”</a> 。该剧还邀请了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megadeth-drummer-dirk-verbeuren-the-killers-mr-brightside-3469205">Megadeth 的鼓手挑战 The Killers 的“Mr.”。 Brightside&#39;</a>和音乐神童<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nandi-bushell">Nandi Bushell</a>为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/twisted-sister">Twisted Sister</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-nandi-bushell-play-drums-to-twisted-sisters-were-not-gonna-take-it-as-she-hears-it-for-first-time-3558476">&#39;We&#39;re Not Gonna Take It&#39; 打鼓，而他们以前从未听过这首歌</a>。</p><p>以各种形式存在了 35 年的蓝人乐队 (Blue Man Group) 与音乐总监乔什·马修斯 (Josh Matthews) 一起前往纽约接受挑战。当马修斯在第一次聆听时做笔记时，蓝人乐队正在进行戏剧表演。</p><p>当演奏这首歌时，乐队使用了一系列非常规的物体作为打击乐器，包括 PVC 管和桶鼓，而马修斯则演奏传统的鼓组。</p><p>看看下面： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="蓝人乐团首次听到“欢迎来到黑人游行”" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/P9DIm2L7gWQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reunion-hopes-dashed-as-my-chemical-romance-confirm-their-facebook-was-hacked-dont-believe-everything-you-read-3778839">今年早些时候，在他们的 Facebook 上出现了一系列奇怪的帖子后，“我的化学浪漫”(My Chemical Romance) 的重聚希望破灭了</a>。当乐队继续发布一些奇怪的帖子时，人们的怀疑越来越多， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/have-my-chemical-romance-been-hacked-or-is-it-part-of-a-comeback-3778501">导致粉丝们质疑是否即将举行合法的重聚，或者他们是否遭到了黑客攻击</a>。</p><p>他们在 Instagram 上写道：“我们的 Facebook 被黑了”，并警告粉丝：“不要相信你读到的一切！”</p><p>这些情绪摇滚偶像<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/my-chemical-romance-fans-react-as-the-band-plays-final-show-of-their-reunion-tour-setlist-3420587">于今年三月结束了漫长的重聚巡演</a>。他们的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/my-chemical-romance-los-angeles-reunion-gig-review-setlist-watch-2590495">首场演出于 2019 年 12 月举行</a>，去年夏天<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/my-chemical-romance-deeply-sad-postpone-2021-tour-dates-2022-2922445">，他们因新冠疫情而推迟的世界巡演</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/my-chemical-romance-debut-new-music-and-rarities-at-first-uk-show-in-11-years-3226970">以在康沃尔郡 The Eden Project 的两场演出</a>开始。</p><p>该乐队最新的作品是 2022 年的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-my-chemical-romances-new-song-the-foundations-of-decay-lyrics-listen-3224304">The Foundations of Decay</a> 》，这是一首令人惊喜的单曲，标志着他们八年来的首张新专辑，他们的最后一张完整专辑是 2010 年的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-my-chemical-romance-11724-322210">Danger Days</a> 》。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-blue-man-group-cover-my-chemical-romances-welcome-to-the-black-parade-after-one-listen-3784575">观看 Blue Man Group 翻唱 My Chemical Romance 的“Welcome to the Black Parade”后，</a>先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上听一听。</p> ;
